summary.problem: Users want to access Corn and Soybean FOB and CNF price data via the platform's API but cannot find the relevant datasets in the dataset list.
summary.solution: The FOB and CNF price data for Corn and Soybeans are available via the API under specific dataset codes. For World Corn CNF Updates, use the dataset code 'vam-a410fb85-d8ab-11ef-82fc-06cd53a4d901'. For Soybean world CNF daily data, use the dataset code 'vam-b327c07f-efd6-11ef-bba5-0a84c630a3f1'. Users can query these datasets through the API to retrieve the relevant FOB and CNF price information.
